<h2>Supported form controls</h2>
<p>Examples of standard form controls supported in an example form layout.</p>

<h3>Standard HTML5 inputs</h3>
<p>Most common form control, text-based input fields. Includes support for all HTML5 types: <em>text, password, datetime, datetime-local, date, month, time, week, number, email, url, search, tel, file and color</em>.</p>
<p>Requires the use of a specified <code>type</code> at all times.</p>
<div class="dive-docs-example ">
<form >
<input type="text" placeholder="Text input">
<br>
<input type="password" placeholder="Password input">  <br>
<input type="range" min="0"     max="10"     step="1"    value="6">  <br>
<input type="file">

</form>
</div>
